I am now a little more then a month sober off alcohol and drugs and trying my best to live up to my promises for God and myself and family as best I can without being discouraged as life throws unexpected curve balls testing your faith/promises in this case I've made to God. I went to Church again by myself today and am actively trying to not break the promises I had made for that prayer being heard.

Thanks for reading if you did, Godbless
